General.Name: Yinson Holdings Bhd
General.Description: Yinson Holdings Berhad, an investment holding company, operates as a floating, production, storage, and offloading (FPSO) service provider. The company operates through Offshore Production & Offshore Marine, Renewables, and Other operations segments. It designs, constructs, leases, and sub-leases FPSO on a bareboat or time charter basis, as well as offers related operation and maintenance services; builds, owns, and operates renewable generating assets; sells electricity; and owns, operates, and charters offshore support vessels and tankers. The company also offers management, treasury management, work permit, and business and management consultancy services. In addition, the company provides ship management services; floating marine assets for chartering and service activities incidental to oil and gas extraction; and engineering design and consultancy services relating to the offshore oil and gas industry. The company was founded in 1983 and is headquartered in Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia.
